OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1773087073
OL,3,CMultiple arrests made following
OL,4,Cprotests in Bristol
OL,6,FMultiple arrests have taken place
OL,7,Ffollowing disorder during a planned
OL,8,Fprotest and counter-protest in Bristol
OL,9,Fcity centre.
OL,11,FThe protest group had approximately 40
OL,12,Fpeople in attendance, with around 200
OL,13,Fcounter-protesters also present.
OL,15,FAvon and Somerset Police says: "During
OL,16,Fthe march, officers experienced a
OL,17,Fnumber of points of resistance, with
OL,18,Fdisorder breaking out between the two-
OL,19,Fsides and items being thrown at
OL,20,Fofficers.
OL,26,@wD@`OU
