OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1773087073
OL,3,CMultiple arrests made following
OL,4,Cprotests in Bristol
OL,6,F"Utilising additional resources,
OL,7,Fofficers were required to use
OL,8,Fproportionate force to ensure the
OL,9,Fsafety of all individuals involved and
OL,10,Fkeeping the groups apart, this
OL,11,Fincluded the use of batons and horses
OL,12,Ffrom the mounted unit to push back
OL,13,Fcrowds."
OL,15,FMore than 200 police officers were in
OL,16,Fthe city centre including mutual aid
OL,17,Fresources from Wiltshire,
OL,18,FGloucestershire and Devon and Cornwall
OL,19,FPolice.
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@HO]
