PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1773087073
OL,3,CMultiple arrests made following
OL,4,Cprotests in Bristol
OL,6,FSix arrests were made during the
OL,7,Fprotest and all suspects were taken
OL,8,Finto police custody. The arrests were
OL,9,Fas follows:
OL,11,FNeighbour Policing Inspector John
OL,12,FShaddick said: "Today's protests in
OL,13,FBristol were closely planned for and
OL,14,Factively managed by our policing
OL,15,Fteams. Our priority throughout was
OL,16,Fclear: to facilitate the right to
OL,17,Fpeaceful protest while keeping the
OL,18,Fpublic, businesses, and participants
OL,19,Fsafe.
OL,26,@tD@POU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/4
