FL,439,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1773087073
OL,3,CMultiple arrests made following
OL,4,Cprotests in Bristol
OL,6,F"There were periods of disruption
OL,7,Fcaused by a small number of
OL,8,Findividuals. Where behaviour crossed
OL,9,Fthe line into disorder, officers acted
OL,10,Fproportionately and used appropriate
OL,11,Fforce to quickly regain control and
OL,12,Fprevent further harm.
OL,14,F"A number of arrests were made for
OL,15,Fpublic order offences and related
OL,16,Fmatters, these will now be subject to
OL,17,Fthe normal investigative processes."
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@AOU
